---
title: Crispy Sweet Dijon Chicken Thighs with Wild Rice and Glazed Veggies
description: Brown sugar and Dijon mustard are the stars of this dish! Together, they add pops of sweet Dijon flavour to chicken topped with golden, crispy panko and our veggie medley.
